            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Our "Indescreet" Governor</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>Never, perhaps, was there a more striking exemplification of the
                    instability of political opinion, and the unreliability of politicians, than has
                    been furnished in the history of Kansas affairs, especially here in Virginia.</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Discusses Kansas politics, regional distinctions, Douglas's political
                    actions.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>A New Feature</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>The more internal improvement the less Democractic heresy.</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Announces new section in "Vindicator" addressing internal
                improvements.</summary>
            </div>
