                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>George Kenton Harper, Esq., 79, died in Chambersburg on 1/28/1858. As a War
                    of 1812 officer, participated in invasion of Canada and defence of Baltimore. He
                    is the father of Capt. Kenton Harper of Augusta County.</summary>
            </div>
